bug.short_desc: Scrollbar of tree overlays internal Windows and Menus

long_desc.thetext:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the showcase demo on Firefox (1.5 or 2.0) on Mac OSX 2. Click the Themes Icon (http://demo.qooxdoo.org/0.7-beta2/showcase/#Themes) 3. Click the button "Open theming window" 4. Click the "Tree" Icon 5. Now the Scrollbar of the tree overlays the Theme window.
Same with Menus. Please fix this bug asap.
